<item>
            <title>[LU-7375] el6.7 case missing from lbuild function</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7375</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the el6.7 case is missing from one of the auto detect functions in lbuild.  this means that when building for el6.7 the --target option must be present on the command line.  This isn&apos;t true for any other distro.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Simple oversight that prevents automatic detection of the right target on el6.7 builds.  I will push a patch to fix this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
